[14/04/2019 22:18:27] <font color="#00ff00">el plano secuencia</font>
[14/04/2019 22:18:28] <font color="#00ff00">que quería Luis.</font>
[14/04/2019 22:18:30] <font color="#ffffff">-Que me despeino.</font>
[14/04/2019 22:18:30] <font color="#00ff00">Eh... Gamero, Florentino</font>
